Info.Title: Changeling
Info.Genre: Biography, Crime, Drama, History, Mystery, Thriller
Info.Actors: Angelina Jolie, Gattlin Griffith, Michelle Gunn, Jan Devereaux
Info.Plot: Grief-stricken mother Christine Collins (Angelina Jolie) takes on the L.A.P.D. to her own detriment when it tries to pass off an obvious impostor as her missing child.
Info.Awards: Nominated for 3 Oscars. Another 14 wins & 50 nominations.
